snippet.title: Arcade Game: Jack Rabbit (1984 Zaccaria)
snippet.description:
A platform run 'n jump game where you as a rabbit to collect carrots while being chased by weasels.

You must move the joystick diagonally to move the rabbit. This how the game works.

Note: The game is endless. Used Invincibility cheat after down to last life.
